        {
            "title": "大阪世博｜中國公民操縱無人機飛行 警查有無獲得許可",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"大阪世博即將開幕。法新社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a9adb8cb6ccc2af6575849ad6ac12db4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250411/_2025041122400166499.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">大阪世博即將開幕。法新社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>2025年世界博覽會周六（12日）下午將在大阪灣的人工島夢洲會場舉行開幕式。11日傍晚，有警察發現無人機飛行，經了解是由一名與世博會相關的中國人操縱，警方已收回無人機並進行調查。\n\n</p>\n<p>為預防應對恐襲等緊急狀況，世博會場及周邊範圍約半徑1公里原則上禁止無人機飛行，若要用無人機，需事先向世博協會等相關機構申請。據悉該架無人機在中國館附近飛行。警方正在向該名中國公民詢問細節，包括是否已提出申請。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"大阪世博將於4月12日舉行開幕式，圖為中國館。法新社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dfff21d377449692e749e85fff4291c3/2025-04/a4_7.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大阪世博將於4月12日舉行開幕式，圖為中國館。法新社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"大阪世博在大阪灣的人工島夢洲會場舉行。美聯社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6202ca5908acbbacda075aaed5752abf/2025-04/k2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大阪世博在大阪灣的人工島夢洲會場舉行。美聯社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"民眾手持世博吉祥物。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6a9e6c96005f3d86dd0fce890eb8dedb/2025-04/a1_16.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        民眾手持世博吉祥物。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"大阪世博會中國館。　世博會中國館微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f10880bf5060c299e3422d8e2d22794c/2025-04/0403011.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大阪世博會中國館。　世博會中國館微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"大阪世博會中國館。　世博會中國館微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fc758ba8aa37f6137a003f5d1bc43e83/2025-04/0403006.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大阪世博會中國館。　世博會中國館微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"大阪世博會中國館。　世博會中國館微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https: